	<div id="t_208_50" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:36.45%;" class="c_208_4">
		AMENDMENT 16. Status of Income Tax Clarified. <span class="c_208_5">Ratified 2/3/1913.</span>
	</div>

	<div id="t_208_51" style="position: absolute; left: 33.68%; top:37.97%;" class="c_208_3">
		The Congress shall have power to lay and collect taxes on incomes, from whatever
	</div>

	<div id="t_208_52" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:39.49%;" class="c_208_3">
