	<div id="t_208_66" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:62.68%;" class="c_208_4">
		AMENDMENT 18. Making, Selling, and Distributing Liquor. <span class="c_208_5">Ratified</span>
	</div>

	<div id="t_208_67" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:64.20%;" class="c_208_3">
