	</div>

	<div id="t_208_68" style="position: absolute; left: 33.68%; top:65.71%;" class="c_208_3">
		1. After one year from the ratification of this article the manufacture, sale, or
	</div>

	<div id="t_208_69" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:67.23%;" class="c_208_3">
		transportation of intoxicating liquors within, the importation thereof into, or the
	</div>

	<div id="t_208_70" style="position: absolute; left: 32.21%; top:68.74%;" class="c_208_3">
